        "creation_date": 1672241928,
        "body": "<p>Looks like OP's issue was different from mine, but the error it produced was the same. Incase anyone else stumbles across this incredibly annoying issue...<\/p>\n<p>Basically I was trying to install the elastic stack and Grafana on the same LXC container in proxmox. Grafana and elastic cannot be installed on the same LXC container because Grafana requires nesting to be enabled, but elastic doesn't work when nesting is enabled.<\/p>\n<p>So long answer short, disable nesting on the LXC container.<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 74942163,
        "question_id": 73630652
    }],
